'''The University of Texas Health Science Center at Houston''' was created by the [[University of Texas System|UT System Board of Regents]] and supported by the [[Texas Legislature]] in 1972. Located in the world-renowned [[Texas Medical Center]], the school is primarily a graduate education university focusing on the [[health sciences]].
